quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  2,1,"Alif, Lām, Meem.{1}",footnotes:1:1
  2,2,"This is the Book about which there is no doubt, a guidance for those conscious of Allāh{1} -",footnotes:1:1
  2,3,"Who believe in the unseen, establish prayer,{1} and spend out of what We{2} have provided for them,",footnotes:1:1,footnotes:2:2
  2,4,"And who believe in what has been revealed to you, [O Muḥammad], and what was revealed before you, and of the Hereafter they are certain [in faith]."
  2,5,"Those are upon [right] guidance from their Lord, and it is those who are the successful."